{"article_id":"lF55DorrSbEqz9wH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Wisconsin Gov . Scott Walker endorsed Sen. Ted Cruz for president Tuesday ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"giving Mr. Cruz a major boost ahead of the April 5 GOP primary in the Badger State .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"\" I am proud to endorse Ted Cruz , \"","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Mr. Walker said on WTMJ radio .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"\" After a lot of time","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"looking at speeches ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"looking at the records ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"looking at what the candidates not only say","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"but what they have done in the past ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"it was an easy call for me to support Ted Cruz . \"","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Many Republicans in recent weeks","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"who have endorsed or supported Mr. Cruz","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"have cited stopping GOP front-runner Donald Trump as part of their calculus .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"But Mr. Walker said","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"he wanted to make sure","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"he was supporting someone","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and that he wasn ' t against something or someone .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Mr. Walker ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"who called Mr. Cruz a \" constitutional conservative \"","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"capable of taking on special interests ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"the Texas senator is best positioned","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"both to win the GOP nomination and defeat Democratic front-runner Hillary Clinton in the fall .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Mr. Walker said","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"he got to know Mr. Cruz a bit better during the campaign .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"\" He is a decent man ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"he loves his family ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"he loves his wife -","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"he adores his children , \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Mr. Walker said .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"\" He loves his country .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"He and I are both preacher ' s kids ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"so I certainly can appreciate and feel strongly about the impact","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"that his father had on him as a minister . \"","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Walker also pointed out","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that he and Mr. Cruz , 45 , are both in their 40s , as is House Speaker Paul D. Ryan , 46 ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"who is also from Wisconsin .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"\" We actually literally came of age under President Ronald Reagan ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and I just see someone","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"who ' s willing to uphold those same principles ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"and that ' s why I ' m proud to endorse , \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"said Mr. Walker , 48 .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"In a statement , Mr. Cruz said","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Walker has been \" an outstanding leader in the conservative movement . \"","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"\" Gov . Walker courageously stood up to special interests","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and won in a bitter fight in Wisconsin , \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Mr. Cruz said .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"\" His leadership has made a profound impact on the people of Wisconsin","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and I welcome his advice","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"on how we can unite the Republican party","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and defeat Hillary Clinton in November . \"","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. Cruz , along with Mr. Trump and Ohio Gov . John Kasich , are in Wisconsin this week","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"trying to build support ahead of the state ' s primary next Tuesday .","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"Mr. Walker said","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"he does anticipate campaigning with Mr. Cruz ahead of the primary next week .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"\" To me , I ' m all in , \"","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Mr. Walker said .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"\" This is not a default . \"","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"Mr. Walker had strongly hinted","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"he was thinking about endorsing Mr. Cruz in an interview last week with WTMJ ,","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"his views would probably be more aligned with those of Mr. Cruz or Mr. Kasich","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"as opposed to Mr. Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"but that Mr. Cruz was better positioned than Mr. Kasich in terms of the delegate math .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"When he suspended his own presidential campaign in September ,","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"Mr. Walker had also encouraged other candidates to think about dropping out","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"so voters could focus on a smaller number of candidates","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"\" who can offer a positive conservative alternative to the current front-runner . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":135,"left":118,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":77,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":69,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":70,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":4,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":5,"right":72,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":6,"right":71,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":89,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":83,"right":88,"relation":"adversati